These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana, bongani, bluemaster, chaman, bolivar, davidoff
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, comedy, musical, animation, sports, action, scientific
City: edinburgh, new-york, san-francisco, marseilles, miami, liverpool, hamburg
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, turtle, chinchilla, frog, cat, hamster
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the owner of the frog is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the havana-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the hamster and the person watching action movies##2
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the bongani-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is the chaman-smoker##1
12. the chaman-smoker is the owner of the goldfish##1
13. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is the owner of the turtle##1
15. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
16. the havana-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
17. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
18. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
19. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Cigar      | havana  | bolivar        | chaman | bongani      | bluemaster     | dunhill      | davidoff     |
